#  AI-Enhanced Real-Time Dashboard â€“ Backend (Node.js + Express + MongoDB)

This is the **backend** of the AI-Enhanced MERN Real-Time Dashboard and Flowchart Editor. Built using **Node.js**, **Express**, **MongoDB**, and **Socket.IO**, this service handles:

-  OTP-based authentication
-  Real-time sensor data simulation & broadcast
-  Flowchart saving, loading, and updating
-  JWT-secured endpoints
-  AI-assisted logic and architecture

---

##  Tech Stack

- ðŸ”¹ Node.js + Express
- ðŸ”¹ MongoDB + Mongoose
- ðŸ”¹ Socket.IO for real-time communication
- ðŸ”¹ Nodemailer for OTP via email
- ðŸ”¹ JWT for route protection
- ðŸ”¹ dotenv for environment config
- ðŸ”¹ AI Tools: ChatGPT, GitHub Copilot

---

##  Features

###  Auth API

- `POST /register` â€“ Register user
- `POST /register/:otp` â€“ Verify OTP sent via email
- `POST /login` â€“ Login with credentials
- `GET /fetch/profile` â€“ Get user profile (JWT protected)

### ðŸ“¡ Data API

- `POST /api/data/start` â€“ Start the real-time sensor simulator
- `POST /api/data/stop` â€“ Stop simulator

> Sensor emits values via Socket.IO every 1â€“2 seconds.

###  Flow API

- `POST /flow/save` â€“ Save flowchart (nodes & edges)
- `GET /flow/load` â€“ Load saved flowchart

